A '''Mentop''' was the name given to the spiritual and [[Psychiatrist|psychiatric]] advisors to the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]]. During the height of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], their goal was to watch over the mental health and stability of the [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] [[Clone trooper/Legends|troopers]] that were produced on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]].

[[Glorii Profus]] was a mentop.

